  "body_html": "<div class=\"hero\">\n    <img src=\"https://dailycoffee.matrix.com.tw/article/coffee-stopover/hero.jpg\" alt=\"COFFEE STOPOVER 咖啡店\">\n    <img class=\"logo-stamp\" src=\"https://dailycoffee.matrix.com.tw/article/coffee-stopover/logo.jpg\" alt=\"COFFEE STOPOVER Logo\">\n \n  <div class=\"hero-overlay\">\n      <div class=\"cat-badge\">咖啡地圖</div>\n      <h1>COFFEE STOPOVER</h1>\n      <div class=\"article-meta\">\n        <span>☕ 2015 自家烘焙</span>\n        <span>📍 台中市西區</span>\n        <span>🏭 兩間分店</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"content\">\n\n    <h2>一號店｜COFFEE STOPOVER</h2>\n    <div class=\"info-grid\">\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">🕐</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">營業時間</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">週一 ~ 週六 11:00–20:00（週日公休）</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">📍</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">地址</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=COFFEE+STOPOVER+台中市西區民權路217巷24號\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            台中市西區民權路 217 巷 24 號\n          </a>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">☎️</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">電話</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\"><a href=\"tel:+886-4-2305-5388\">04-2305-5388</a></span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">☕</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">萃取方式</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">手衝 · 義式濃縮</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">🛒</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">販售商品</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">單品豆 · 配方豆 · 茶咖啡濾掛 · 特殊配方豆</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>二號店｜COFFEE STOPOVER BLACK</h2>\n    <div class=\"info-grid\">\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">🕐</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">營業時間</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">週二 ~ 週六 14:00–19:00（週日週一公休）</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">📍</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">地址</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=COFFEE+STOPOVER+BLACK+台中市西區福龍街7號\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            台中市西區福龍街 7 號\n          </a>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">☎️</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">電話</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\"><a href=\"tel:+886-4-2208-0580\">04-2208-0580</a></span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">☕</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">萃取方式</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">拉霸式義式濃縮 · 愛樂壓 · 法國壓 · 賽風</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"info-row\">\n        <span class=\"info-icon\">🛒</span>\n        <span class=\"info-label\">販售商品</span>\n        <span class=\"info-value\">單品豆 · 配方豆 · 茶咖啡濾掛 · 特殊配方豆 · 咖啡選物</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"social-row\">\n      <a class=\"social-btn\" href=\"https://www.coffeestopover.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z\"/></svg>\n        官方網站\n      </a>\n      <a class=\"social-btn\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/coffeestopover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M7.8 2h8.4C19.4 2 22 4.6 22 7.8v8.4a5.8 5.8 0 0 1-5.8 5.8H7.8C4.6 22 2 19.4 2 16.2V7.8A5.8 5.8 0 0 1 7.8 2m-.2 2A3.6 3.6 0 0 0 4 7.6v8.8C4 18.39 5.61 20 7.6 20h8.8a3.6 3.6 0 0 0 3.6-3.6V7.6C20 5.61 18.39 4 16.4 4H7.6m9.65 1.5a1.25 1.25 0 0 1 1.25 1.25A1.25 1.25 0 0 1 17.25 8 1.25 1.25 0 0 1 16 6.75a1.25 1.25 0 0 1 1.25-1.25M12 7a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5m0 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0 3 3 3 3 0 0 0 3-3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"/></svg>\n        @coffeestopover\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tag-row\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">#自家烘焙</span>\n      <span class=\"tag\">#台中咖啡</span>\n      <span class=\"tag\">#精品咖啡</span>\n      <span class=\"tag\">#單品豆</span>\n      <span class=\"tag\">#配方豆</span>\n      <span class=\"tag\">#咖啡選物</span>\n      <span class=\"tag\">#街區咖啡</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>為什麼值得專程來</h2>\n    <p>COFFEE STOPOVER 起站於 2015 年夏末，是台中具代表性的自家烘焙精品咖啡品牌。兩間分店風格各異——一號店走低調悠閒的街區工業風，手充吧檯直面客人；二號店 BLACK 走濃黑系實驗風，結合烘豆基地，萃取方式從義式到賽風應有盡有。</p>\n    <p>品牌精神是「打破常規」，菜單上可以自由選擇咖啡豆、焙度、濾杯與沖煮方式，由咖啡師為你量身訂做專屬咖啡。這種高度客製化的體驗，是許多咖啡愛好者一再回訪的原因。</p>\n\n    <div class=\"spotlight\">\n      <div class=\"spotlight-title\">☕ 這裡適合什麼人</div>\n      <p>想自由度高一點、願意跟咖啡師討論風味偏好、喜歡動手玩咖啡的人。一號店適合悠閒坐坐，二號店 BLACK 則適合對咖啡有更深度研究興趣的玩家。</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2>推薦品項</h2>\n    <p>兩間店各有擅場：<b>一號店</b>推薦手充單品，可以品嚐到明亮的水果調性與發酵香；<b>二號店 BLACK</b>則推薦用愛樂壓或賽風沖煮的浸泡式咖啡，厚實沉穩、風味集中。別忘了逛逛二號店的咖啡選物區，品牌聯名周邊時有驚喜。</p>\n\n    <h2>遊客回饋</h2>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"reviewer\">咖啡探索者</div>\n      <p>「第一次來的時候被菜單搞懵了——可以選豆子、焙度、濾杯！後來跟咖啡師聊了一下，他推薦了一支中焙的配方豆，做成手充非常好喝，從此成了常客。」</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"reviewer\">咖啡器材迷</div>\n      <p>「二號店 BLACK 超適合我，濃黑系裝潢、烘豆機就在旁邊，還可以買到各種咖啡器材。周邊聯名商品也很有創意，買過一次濾掛禮盒送朋友。」</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <a class=\"map-link\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=COFFEE+STOPOVER+台中市西區民權路217巷24號\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\"><path d=\"M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z\"/></svg>\n      Google Maps 開啟地圖\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"back-link\" href=\"https://dailycoffee.matrix.com.tw\">← 返回首頁</a>\n  </div>",
